    <item>
      <title>斗山集团以中端价格在捷克罕见首次公开募股中出售子公司股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/doosan-sells-unit-stake-in-rare-czech-ipo-at-mid-range-price</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斗山能源公司 (Doosan Enerbility Co.) 通过首次公开募股 (IPO) 出售了其捷克蒸汽轮机部门的股份，发行价处于目标区间的中间水平，成为布拉格四年多以来规模最大的新上市交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/doosan-sells-unit-stake-in-rare-czech-ipo-at-mid-range-price</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 06:57:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行上调盈利目标，计划派发 17 亿欧元股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/socgen-announces-1-7-billion-investor-payout-as-profit-beats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行宣布去年向投资者支付 17 亿欧元（18 亿美元），因为受法国零售银行业务复苏的推动，第四季度利润超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/socgen-announces-1-7-billion-investor-payout-as-profit-beats</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 05:32:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
